      <textAnnotation id="sid-13CC5ABC-F2D5-4C39-9FE9-6FBD49BF231A" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Return related boundary apps not applicable for R2 and R3 (e.g. TCA, CATTS, SAP TM, Fraud Detection, Entitlement Management)
Only Manual creation by CBA with key information on batch  number. 
Order can be created with or without reference to original invoice.
Incase original order is in ECC, then it will require manual maintenance of information in S4 Returns order.
Return Order will be created on the same plant where product was originally issued from.
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <group categoryValueRef="sid-34467b3e-fe56-4b0b-acd7-d1a77b6bd332" id="sid-DDA9CB34-20D2-4669-915B-AB949F87DBCF">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel align="center" ref="text_name" valign="middle" x="41.0" y="-12.0"/>
         </extensionElements>
      </group>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-41D5820E-13CA-4825-9FEA-D2416B392A7F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Notes:
1.Return related boundary apps not applicable for R2.
2.Only Manual creation by CBA with key information on batch  number. 
3.Order can be created with or without reference to original invoice.
4.Incase original order is in ECC, then it will require manual maintenance of information in S4 Returns order.
5.Return Order will be created on the same plant where product was originally issued from.
6. SAP EMS, TCA, CATTS and Fraud Detection app are not in scope for R2/R3 for Returns Process
7. SAP TM – Embedded(Returns Out of Scope for R2)
8. Initiate Return to Customer process in-case of discrepant/unacceptable / no remedy / out of warranty product and customer agreed for return instead of waster processing at Intel Site. </text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
